  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046150/extras/aa9f2f0a72b191afc0cd1279ac070e39.avif?t=1763053529\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046150/extras_big/aa9f2f0a72b191afc0cd1279ac070e39.avif?t=1763053529 width=800 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Following the death of a family matriarch, the surviving heirs return from abroad to their childhood home in The Berkshires. But in addition to the family’s Victorian mansion, sprawling acreage, and millions of dollars, they’ve also inherited something much more sinister. A spooky masked figure appears and warns the siblings that they will be the next victims of a grizzly family curse dating back to the Gilded Age. After another fatality on the property, the prophecy is seemingly proven true. Can you help Cleo and Detective Guy crack the mystery of multiple murders and a 150-year-old legend? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- stand-alone murder mystery whodunit RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- play as a detective and dog crime-solving team</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- explore the area and look for clues</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- interview suspects and make deductions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- solve the case and apprehend the guilty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- optional horror gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- new \"open world\" design.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046150/extras/aa9f2f0a72b191afc0cd1279ac070e39.avif?t=1763053529\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046150/extras_big/aa9f2f0a72b191afc0cd1279ac070e39.avif?t=1763053529 width=800 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Following the death of a family matriarch, the surviving heirs return from abroad to their childhood home in The Berkshires. But in addition to the family’s Victorian mansion, sprawling acreage, and millions of dollars, they’ve also inherited something much more sinister. A spooky masked figure appears and warns the siblings that they will be the next victims of a grizzly family curse dating back to the Gilded Age. After another fatality on the property, the prophecy is seemingly proven true. Can you help Cleo and Detective Guy crack the mystery of multiple murders and a 150-year-old legend? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- stand-alone murder mystery whodunit RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- play as a detective and dog crime-solving team</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- explore the area and look for clues</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- interview suspects and make deductions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- solve the case and apprehend the guilty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- optional horror gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- new \"open world\" design.</p>",
